videos.headline: Sharpe slams the alley-oop from Love
videos.description: Caleb Love tosses up an alley-oop to Day'Ron Sharpe for the two-handed jam to extend UNC's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sharpe slams the alley-oop from Love) 2020/12/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Keyser shows no mercy on the rim with thunderous slam
videos.description: North Carolina Central's Justin Whatley dishes to a cutting C.J. Keyser who rises for the vicious one-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (C.J. Keyser shows no mercy on the rim with thunderous slam) 2020/12/12 ESHEET
